(70, 1, '2014-11-04 05:48:06', '2014-11-04 05:48:06', '<div class="con-block" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n\r\n<img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-192" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/vadodara-unit-300x116.jpg" alt="vadodara-unit" width="300" height="116" />The <strong>Vadodara</strong> unit is located at Savli in GIDC complex and has a land area of 100,700 m² with 42,500 m² covered. The region falls on the Savli-Halol route of the Delhi Mumbai Investment Corridor (DMIC), NH 8. Savli has been recognised as a location for Export Promotion Industrial Park (EPIP) which is proposed to be elevated to the Special Economic Zone (SEZ). The nearest deep sea port is Dahej, 150 kms away and the nearest airport is Vadodara, 14 kms away.\r\n\r\nThis unit has four bays each 26 mtr wide and 150 m long with 13 m hook height and 100 tons crane handling facility.The flooring is of RCC tri-mix capable of handling large loads. The open yard is approximately 35000 sqmtrs. Apart from the manufacturing bays, the unit has a fully furnished Office Block of 1082 sqmtrs and a separate modern canteen block. Power connection is from 33 kV HT line through a 1000 kVA transformer.\r\n\r\nThe unit is ISO 9001 certified.\r\n\r\nThis unit has a dedicated Design team and is equipped with all kinds of manufacturing facilities for fabrication, machining, assembly, inspection and testing.\r\n\r\nThe Vadodara unit manufactures “SAYAJI” brand of jaw crushers, roll crushers, hammer mills, impactors, coke cutters, various types of screens and wheel mounted crushing and screening plant.It has alsostarted manufacturing of Concrete Batching Plant, Asphalt Batching Plant and Dry Mortar Mixing Plant of various capacities with the technology provided by Fujian South Highway Machinery Co. Ltd. (NFLG).\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class="ngg_displayed_gallery mceItem" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/nextgen-attach_to_post/preview/id--1184" alt="" data-mce-placeholder="1" />\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Vadodara', 'The Vadodara unit is located at Savli in GIDC complex and has a land area of 100,700 m² with 42,500 m² covered.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'vadodara', '', '', '2015-05-19 07:41:39', '2015-05-19 07:41:39', '', 0, 'http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/?post_type=manufacture&#038;p=70', 0, 'manufacture', '', 0),
