(173, 1, '2014-11-07 04:02:00', '2014-11-07 04:02:00', '<h3>Celebrations galore</h3>\r\n24th Deepawali cum Motelian Nite was organized by Sports and Cultural Council of MSEL at our factory. The whole event created a festive environment in the organization and brought everybody together as one.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_265" align="alignleft" width="300"]<img class="size-full wp-image-265" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic6.jpg" alt="Lights and Festivities: 24th Deepawali cum Motelian Nite Celebration" width="300" height="200" /> Lights and Festivities: 24th Deepawali cum<br />Motelian Nite Celebration[/caption]</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_269" align="alignleft" width="300"]<img class="size-full wp-image-269" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic2.jpg" alt="The colorful and traditional Dandiya dance organized by Colony Ladies" width="300" height="200" /> The colorful and traditional Dandiya dance<br />organized by Colony Ladies[/caption]</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class="clr"></div>\r\n<h3>Grand celebration on Republic Day &amp; Independence Day</h3>\r\nMSEL celebrated Republic Day &amp; Independence Day of our country in a grand manner charged with dignity, motivation and patriotism.\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_268" align="alignleft" width="250"]<img class="size-full wp-image-268" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic3.jpg" alt="National Flag Hoisting on the occasion of Republic Day &amp; Independence Day" width="250" height="291" /> National Flag Hoisting on the occasion<br />of Republic Day &amp; Independence Day[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_267" align="alignleft" width="620"]<img class="size-full wp-image-267" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic16.jpg" alt="Annual Sports Meet organized by Ladies Wing at one of our factories for all the sports enthusiasts" width="620" height="208" /> Annual Sports Meet organized by Ladies Wing at one of our factories for all the sports enthusiasts[/caption]\r\n\r\n<div class="clr"></div>\r\n<h3>Honouring the staff with Long Service Awards</h3>\r\nDistribution of long service awards by Mr. Subir Chaki, Wholetime Director was awarded to our workmen and management staff for their committed long association with our organization.\r\n\r\n<img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-266" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic5.jpg" alt="life-at-msel-pic5" width="300" height="200" />\r\n\r\n<img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-265" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic6.jpg" alt="life-at-msel-pic6" width="300" height="200" />\r\n<div class="clr"></div>\r\n<h3>Fun and frolic on Annual Picnic by employees &amp; their family members</h3>\r\n<img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-264" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic7.jpg" alt="life-at-msel-pic7" width="620" height="244" />\r\n<div class="clr"></div>\r\n<h3>Zero Accident Awards for employees on 42nd National Safety Day</h3>\r\n42nd National Safety Day was celebrated at our factory. Contest was initiated amongst all workmen of the units, for drawing safety cartoons and safety slogans. All winners were recognized for their creative work, with some lucrative gifts. All the departments, who achieved zero accident during last year, were recognized with Zero Accident Award.\r\n\r\n<img class="size-full wp-image-263" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic8.jpg" alt="life-at-msel-pic8" width="300" height="200" />\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_262" align="alignleft" width="300"]<img class="size-full wp-image-262" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic9.jpg" alt="A floral goodbye - Bidding farewell to employees" width="300" height="200" /> A floral goodbye - Bidding farewell to employees[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_261" align="alignleft" width="300"]<img class="size-full wp-image-261" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic10.jpg" alt="Grand Birthday celebrations of employees at office premises" width="300" height="200" /> Grand Birthday celebrations of employees<br />at office premises[/caption]\r\n\r\n<div class="clr"></div>\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_260" align="alignleft" width="300"]<img class="size-full wp-image-260" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic11.jpg" alt="Celebrating the festival of lights with colorful Rangoli at Office" width="300" height="200" /> Celebrating the festival of lights<br />with colorful Rangoli at Office[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_259" align="alignleft" width="300"]<img class="size-full wp-image-259" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic12.jpg" alt="Traditional and festive mood - Celebrating Durga Puja/ Ayudha Puja at the Malur Factory" width="300" height="200" /> Traditional and festive mood - Celebrating Durga Puja/<br />Ayudha Puja at the Malur Factory[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_258" align="alignleft" width="300"]<img class="size-full wp-image-258" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic13.jpg" alt="Welcoming 2013 with cheer! New Year Celebrations at office" width="300" height="200" /> Welcoming 2013 with cheer!<br />New Year Celebrations at office[/caption]\r\n\r\n<div class="clr"></div>\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_257" align="alignleft" width="300"]<img class="size-full wp-image-257" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic14.jpg" alt="Christmas spirit among the employees on the occasion of Merry Christmas" width="300" height="200" /> Christmas spirit among the employees on<br />the occasion of Merry Christmas[/caption]\r\n\r\n<div class="clr"></div>\r\n<a href="#">All India Sales Meet and Product Application Programme at Kumardhubi</a>', 'Life at MSEL', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'life-at-msel', '', '', '2015-05-18 08:08:33', '2015-05-18 08:08:33', '', 7, 'http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/?page_id=173', 0, 'page', '', 0),
