border-right: 1px dashed #015778;" align="center" valign="top"><em><em>ISO</em></em>9001:2008 Certificate\r\nof\r\nAsansol</td>\r\n<td style="border-right: 1px dashed #015778;" align="center" valign="top"><em><em>ISO</em></em>9001:2008 Certificate\r\nof Vadodara</td>\r\n<td style="border-right: 1px dashed #015778;" align="center" valign="top"><em><em>IBR</em></em>Certificate\r\nof\r\n\r\nAsansol</td>\r\n<td style="border-right: 1px dashed #015778;" align="center" valign="top"><em><em>NABL</em></em>Certificate of Kumardhubi</td>\r\n<td align="center" valign="top"><em>Scope of NABL Accreditation - Kumardhubi</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h2>Product Quality</h2>\r\n<h3>QUALITY POLICY</h3>\r\nWe shall consciously strive to upgrade our systems and technology so as to constantly improve our products and services to our customers.\r\n<h3>QUALITY OBJECTIVES</h3>\r\n<strong>We shall –</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Upgrade our technology to improve our products and services.</li>\r\n	<li>Educate and train our employees to enhance the quality of our products.</li>\r\n	<li>Develop vendor base, meeting ourdelivery and quality stipulations.</li>\r\n	<li>Reduce wastage &amp; non-value addedoperations.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Subir Chaki,</strong> Wholetime Director</p>', 'Quality Overview', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '154-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-10 11:04:54', '2014-11-10 11:04:54', '', 154, 'http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/154-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
