(256, 1, '2014-11-10 11:19:14', '2014-11-10 11:19:14', 'Since its inception, MSEL has constantly endeavored to assist the local population around its campus at Kumardhubi.\r\n\r\nMSEL has scholarship scheme for local students. They get trained in various vocations in the neighboring Industrial Training Institute. Subsequently, MSEL also absorbs suitable candidates into its rolls, thereby providing valuable employment in and around socially backward areas.\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_248" align="aligncenter" width="620"]<img class="size-full wp-image-248" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/cdr-pic1.jpg" alt="Students attending Technical Class" width="620" height="240" /> Students attending Technical Class[/caption]\r\n\r\nFrom time to time we arrange technical training to the local students in Computer operation, Tailoring, Carpentry and other traditional trades like Fitter, Electrician, Welding etc. and make them suitable in employment Market.\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_252" align="aligncenter" width="620"]<img src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/cdr-pic2.jpg" alt="Students attending Computer Class" width="620" height="273" class="size-full wp-image-252" /> Students attending Computer Class[/caption]\r\n\r\nMSEL has installed a filtration plant to supply filtered water to the entire village around Kumardhubi.\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_254" align="aligncenter" width="620"]<img src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/cdr-pic3.jpg" alt="Water supply to the villagers" width="620" height="223" class="size-full wp-image-254" /> Water supply to the villagers[/caption]\r\n\r\nPeriodically we organize programmes to create self-help group consisting of village women so that they can help themselves to give First Aid during medical emergencies such as snake bites, epidemics, any accidental case etc.\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_255" align="aligncenter" width="620"]<img src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/cdr-pic4.jpg" alt="Awareness programme for the Self-Help Group" width="620" height="242" class="size-full wp-image-255" /> Awareness programme for the Self-Help Group[/caption]', 'Corporate Social Responsibility', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '156-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-10 11:19:14', '2014-11-10 11:19:14', '', 156, 'http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/156-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
