(271, 1, '2014-11-12 04:20:14', '2014-11-12 04:20:14', '<h3>Celebrations galore</h3>\n24th Deepawali cum Motelian Nite was organized by Sports and Cultural Council of MSEL at our factory. The whole event created a festive environment in the organization and brought everybody together as one.\n<ul>\n<li>[caption id="attachment_265" align="alignleft" width="300"]<img src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic6.jpg" alt="Lights and Festivities: 24th Deepawali cum Motelian Nite Celebration" width="300" height="200" class="size-full wp-image-265" /> Lights and Festivities: 24th Deepawali cum<br />Motelian Nite Celebration[/caption]</li>\n\n<li>[caption id="attachment_269" align="aligncenter" width="300"]<img src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic2.jpg" alt="The colorful and traditional Dandiya dance organized by Colony Ladies" width="300" height="200" class="size-full wp-image-269" /> The colorful and traditional Dandiya dance<br />organized by Colony Ladies[/caption]</li>\n</ul>\n<div >\n<h3>Grand celebration on Republic Day & Independence Day</h3>\n\nMSEL celebrated Republic Day & Independence Day of our country in a grand manner charged with dignity, motivation and patriotism.\n\n[caption id="attachment_268" align="aligncenter" width="250"]<img src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic3.jpg" alt="National Flag Hoisting on the occasion of Republic Day &amp; Independence Day" width="250" height="291" class="size-full wp-image-268" /> National Flag Hoisting on the occasion<br />of Republic Day & Independence Day[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_267" align="aligncenter" width="620"]<img src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic16.jpg" alt="Annual Sports Meet organized by Ladies Wing at one of our factories for all the sports enthusiasts" width="620" height="208" class="size-full wp-image-267" /> Annual Sports Meet organized by Ladies Wing at one of our factories for all the sports enthusiasts[/caption]\n\n<h2>Honouring the staff with Long Service Awards</h2>\n\nDistribution of long service awards by Mr. Subir Chaki, Wholetime Director was awarded to our workmen and management staff for their committed long association with our organization.\n\n<img src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic5.jpg" alt="life-at-msel-pic5" width="300" height="200" class="alignleft size-full wp-image-266" />\n\n<img src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic6.jpg" alt="life-at-msel-pic6" width="300" height="200" class="alignleft size-full wp-image-265" />\n\n<h2>Fun and frolic on Annual Picnic by employees & their family members</h2>\n\n<img src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic7.jpg" alt="life-at-msel-pic7" width="620" height="244" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-264" />\n\n<h2>Zero Accident Awards for employees on 42nd National Safety Day </h2>\n\n42nd National Safety Day was celebrated at our factory. Contest was initiated amongst all workmen of the units, for drawing safety cartoons and safety slogans. All winners were recognized for their creative work, with some lucrative gifts. All the departments, who achieved zero accident during last year, were recognized with Zero Accident Award.\n\n<img src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic8.jpg" alt="life-at-msel-pic8" width="300" height="200" class="alignright size-full wp-image-263" />\n\n[caption id="attachment_262" align="alignright" width="300"]<img src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic9.jpg" alt="A floral goodbye - Bidding farewell to employees" width="300" height="200" class="size-full wp-image-262" /> A floral goodbye - Bidding farewell to employees[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_261" align="alignright" width="300"]<img src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic10.jpg" alt="Grand Birthday celebrations of employees at office premises" width="300" height="200" class="size-full wp-image-261" /> Grand Birthday celebrations of employees<br />at office premises[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_260" align="alignright" width="300"]<img src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic11.jpg" alt="Celebrating the festival of lights with colorful Rangoli at Office" width="300" height="200" class="size-full wp-image-260" /> Celebrating the festival of lights<br />with colorful Rangoli at Office[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_259" align="alignright" width="300"]<img src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic12.jpg" alt="Traditional and festive mood - Celebrating Durga Puja/ Ayudha Puja at the Malur Factory" width="300" height="200" class="size-full wp-image-259" /> Traditional and festive mood - Celebrating Durga Puja/<br />Ayudha Puja at the Malur Factory[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_258" align="alignright" width="300"]<img src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic13.jpg" alt="Welcoming 2013 with cheer! New Year Celebrations at office" width="300" height="200" class="size-full wp-image-258" /> Welcoming 2013 with cheer!<br />New Year Celebrations at office[/caption]\n\n[caption id="attachment_257" align="alignleft" width="300"]<img src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/life-at-msel-pic14.jpg" alt="Christmas spirit among the employees on the occasion of Merry Christmas" width="300" height="200" class="size-full wp-image-257" /> Christmas spirit among the employees on