 :: Kumardubi" width="65" height="92" border="0" /></a></td>\r\n<td style="border-right: 1px dashed #015778;" align="center"><a href="javascript:MM_openBrWindow(''http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/002.jpg'','''',''scrollbars=yes, width=680, height=750'');"><img class="bord" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/kumardhubi2-thumb.jpg" alt="ISO 9001:2008 Certificate :: Kumardubi" width="65" height="92" border="0" /></a></td>\r\n<td style="border-right: 1px dashed #015778;" align="center"><a href="javascript:MM_openBrWindow(''http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/003.jpg'','''',''scrollbars=yes, width=680, height=750'');"><img class="bord" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/iso-certificate-asansol-thumb.jpg" alt="ISO 9001:2008 Certificate :: Asansol" width="65" height="92" border="0" /></a></td>\r\n<td style="border-right: 1px dashed #015778;" align="center"><a href="javascript:MM_openBrWindow(''http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/004.jpg'','''',''scrollbars=yes, width=680, height=750'');"><img class="bord" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/vadodara-thumb.jpg" alt="ISO 9001:2008 Certificate :: Vadodara" width="65" height="92" border="0" /></a></td>\r\n<td style="border-right: 1px dashed #015778;" align="center"><a href="javascript:MM_openBrWindow(''http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/005.jpg'','''',''scrollbars=yes, width=680, height=750'');"><img class="bord" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/ibr-certificate-asansole-thumb.jpg" alt="IBR Certificate :: Asansole" width="65" height="92" border="0" /></a></td>\r\n<td style="border-right: 1px dashed #015778;" align="center"><a href="javascript:MM_openBrWindow(''http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/006.jpg'','''',''scrollbars=yes, width=680, height=750'');"><img class="bord" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/nabl-kumardhubi-thumb.jpg" alt="NABL Certificate :: Kumardhubi" width="65" height="92" border="0" /></a></td>\r\n<td align="center"><a href="javascript:MM_openBrWindow(''http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/007.jpg'','''',''scrollbars=yes, width=680, height=750'');"><img class="bord" src="http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/scope-nabl-kumardhubi-thumb.jpg" alt="Scope of NABL Accreditation :: Kumardhubi" width="65" height="92" border="0" /></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="border-right: 1px dashed #015778;" align="center" valign="top"><em><em>ISO</em></em>14001:2004 Certificate\r\nof Kumardhubi</td>\r\n<td style="border-right: 1px dashed #015778;" align="center" valign="top"><em><em>ISO</em></em>9001:2008 Certificate\r\nof Kumardhubi</td>\r\n<td style="border-right: 1px dashed #015778;" align="center" valign="top"><em><em>ISO</em></em>9001:2008 Certificate\r\nof\r\nAsansol</td>\r\n<td style="border-right: 1px dashed #015778;" align="center" valign="top"><em><em>ISO</em></em>9001:2008 Certificate\r\nof Vadodara</td>\r\n<td style="border-right: 1px dashed #015778;" align="center" valign="top"><em><em>IBR</em></em>Certificate\r\nofAsansol</td>\r\n<td style="border-right: 1px dashed #015778;" align="center" valign="top"><em><em>NABL</em></em>Certificate of Kumardhubi</td>\r\n<td align="center" valign="top"><em>Scope of NABL Accreditation - Kumardhubi</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3>Product Quality</h3>\r\n<h4>QUALITY POLICY</h4>\r\nWe shall consciously strive to upgrade our systems and technology so as to constantly improve our products and services to our customers.\r\n<h4>QUALITY OBJECTIVES</h4>\r\n<strong>We shall –</strong>\r\n<ul class="list-arrow">\r\n	<li>Upgrade our technology to improve our products and services.</li>\r\n	<li>Educate and train our employees to enhance the quality of our products.</li>\r\n	<li>Develop vendor base, meeting ourdelivery and quality stipulations.</li>\r\n	<li>Reduce wastage &amp; non-value addedoperations.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Subir Chaki,</strong> Wholetime Director</p>', 'Quality Overview', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '154-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-19 00:04:29', '2015-05-19 00:04:29', '', 154, 'http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/154-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(972, 2, '2015-05-19 00:09:32', '2015-05-19 00:09:32', '<strong>McNally</strong> is a 50 year old trusted house delivering crushers and screens among other equipment for the aggregate, mineral and mining industry. While <strong>McNally</strong> has been the pioneer in the manufacturing equipment for the mineral, mining and beneficiation industry since 1961, <strong>Sayaji</strong> as a brand is synonymous in aggregate crushing ,delivering consistently reliable and quality crushing systems since 1946. It was in 2009 that the two companies merged together to form <strong>McNally Sayaji Engineering Limited (MSEL)</strong>. Today, with four manufacturing locations at <strong>Vadodara</strong>, <strong>Kumardhubi</strong>, <strong>Asansol</strong>, Bengaluru and having large sales &amp; servicing network spread across India, MSEL is one of the most respected companies to render professional services.\n\nFujian South Highway Machinery Co. Ltd. (NFLG) , situated in the southern province of Fujian, is a 20 year old leading construction equipment manufacturing company in China and has several installations all over the world, namely Russia, Europe, Asia, Middle East , Africa, South America  in addition to over 4700 installations in domestic Chinese market.\n\nWe are delighted to announce the formation of a Joint Venture between MSEL &amp; NFLG by the name McNally Sayaji NFLG Construction Equipment Co. Pvt Ltd. The machines will be manufactured at MSEL, Vadodara facility with NFLG designs suitably adapted, with special features over other competitive products to the exacting needs of well informed and demanding Indian customers. Backed by our competent service team at strategic locations all over India, we believe that we can make a difference to our esteemed customer’s business.', 'Associates', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '970-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-05-19 00:09:32', '2015-05-19 00:09:32', '', 970, 'http://dev1.businessprodemo.com/Mcnallybharat/php/970-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
